column2: "What a coincidence, meeting you down here. How are you holding up?"
"It's probably fate that we met up here, so why don't you come along?"
"But, Zeno! We're in the middle of a quest!"
"Besides, our quest is pretty much wrapped up at this point anyway."
"We? I finished up while you were busy running away from all the native creatures."
"I wasn't running away! I was... Fine, do whatever you want!"
"Okay, looks like we got permission. Let's get going, <%me>!"
